[{"Code":"en","Title":"Value Added Tax (VAT)","Slug":"value-added-tax-vat","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"3de4393b-a5f0-4689-bb1b-786604688cfa\">VAT (Value-Added Tax) is a consumption tax applied to goods and services at each stage of production or distribution. The VAT rate varies depending on the country of service, and for Xendit services, fees are generally <strong>VAT-exclusive</strong>, meaning VAT will be added to the fees as applicable.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"96fc9bc1-351c-4379-8f42-f9f1869a8b1a\">VAT applicability by country</h2><p data-block-id=\"22aee218-4dc0-458d-afe4-29c287ba2a90\">Xendit applies VAT to all services in the following countries:</p><ol data-block-id=\"f704f5e7-0c9c-4289-8dde-b782274ffd86\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"712855e5-1fc9-41ec-8c88-5142860875b9\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"e71f381b-ea80-4a22-865b-8b5fd466f8f1\"><strong>Indonesia</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"cdaef5f6-b63e-40c5-b7c2-99ee4ec539b3\"><li data-block-id=\"a69d1814-f174-43cf-b5f2-94b1da3a5a04\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"485b40f7-9248-4632-98dc-a33d74e6c9f0\"><strong>VAT Rate</strong>: 12% (The subtotal is multiplied by 11/12, bringing effective VAT rate to 11%)</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"3982e446-def7-4ebe-a059-620ac8464fc4\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"124bc150-d140-4c77-b3f5-0eaa689b7134\"><strong>Malaysia</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"02247e0f-ee75-4b5f-8464-df4dc0e90010\"><li data-block-id=\"921445d7-542e-4114-a05f-0eebde28b74f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"9f21b5b1-b049-4c27-9216-de16ffc0cbfa\"><strong>VAT Equivalent (SST)</strong>: 0%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"00f4725d-b5a8-4a46-bbe6-553c67a4d0d1\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"a884c8a2-904d-45f2-a187-e6c329a3f481\"><strong>Thailand</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"40470f38-759d-4618-9213-1e691836906a\"><li data-block-id=\"43e47c6d-7d4e-436d-b5f9-400201c30fcb\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"bb866a6a-84e0-4966-94e5-8d552544dd26\"><strong>VAT Rate</strong>: 7%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"b8dfec48-e5b7-4439-977d-39387d8a49f3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"1a179519-ba60-42f2-9c95-d6c7eacd91f2\"><strong>Vietnam</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"d6aea39f-9f54-4d51-8fbb-5b72f1127f20\"><li data-block-id=\"13c7ebfb-ec32-49f8-b58c-f9025dd1ca58\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"7bc138fa-801e-4c8c-acc8-997ebbbedf98\"><strong>VAT Rate</strong>: 10%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"82ac2318-c6af-49c8-ae2d-d4d86330fe10\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"bf6de06f-c1f8-4b5f-83c8-14aa24bfdb3e\"><strong>Philippines</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"36e0d766-97cd-4285-8b29-899702dd6fe0\"><li data-block-id=\"48dd45e0-02b7-4ce0-b2d1-2add4df55d71\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"c331eb3a-6b5d-4d23-a0de-7a2358dca1e5\"><strong>VAT Rate</strong>: 12%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"81b8c5d3-3b68-4bfb-a111-329a0d19426f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"35e1afa5-5160-41f4-86b9-af5435729de0\"><strong>Singapore</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"e21b11b5-19ca-4c07-8682-ad197b40eda1\"><li data-block-id=\"b669980f-a1b8-4ee5-8a35-f03fd5740e2e\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"dd733af9-553f-4b0f-9aa0-21de7b72af5c\"><mark class=\"cd98f987-7aaf-4fee-b18e-9a991e91bd7d\" data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"cd98f987-7aaf-4fee-b18e-9a991e91bd7d\" data-resolved=\"true\"><strong>VAT equivalent </strong></mark><strong>(GST)</strong>: 0%</p></li></ul></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"96a4fcd4-60dd-4689-8017-f937479be7d8\">VAT calculation</h3><p data-block-id=\"e7a7f1c9-f3fe-4275-83df-9fa59e5afd71\">VAT is calculated on the <strong>transaction fee</strong> using the applicable VAT rate for the country where the service is provided.</p><p data-block-id=\"e7a7f1c9-f3fe-4275-83df-9fa59e5afd71\">In case of <a href=\"/v1/docs/transaction-fees\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Direct Deduction</a>, this amount will be directly deducted from the transaction at settlement.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"ma0wqppw-2evlwv-013\">Example calculation (Vietnam)</h4><ul data-block-id=\"ma0wqppw-0o5f3x-014\"><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-88j15p-017\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-kqpqkb-018\"><strong>Fee Rate</strong>: VND 2,500 per transaction</p></li><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-ull3i9-019\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-9f737z-020\"><strong>VAT (10%)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-sl9cbv-023\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-9i5b5n-024\"><strong>Total Fee</strong> and <strong>Total Fee VAT</strong> = <strong>2500 </strong>+ <strong>2500 × 10</strong>% = VND 2,750</p></li></ul><h4 data-block-id=\"6a7af58a-224b-463b-acc7-97041766f626\">Example calculation (Indonesia)</h4><ul data-block-id=\"91499a2f-4421-4c55-8efa-4bf35c5139f7\"><li data-block-id=\"6f57ec42-3cbd-4363-8e7d-6812532c6037\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"4c2d5b3f-caf8-4c88-9130-1f39736b7e58\"><strong>Fee Rate</strong>: IDR 5,000 per transaction</p></li><li data-block-id=\"636a3982-6a06-4ad9-bc07-bcf0988ecd4f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"b427231f-c9dd-4e89-baa2-29d9209da917\"><strong>VAT (12%)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"636a3982-6a06-4ad9-bc07-bcf0988ecd4f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"b427231f-c9dd-4e89-baa2-29d9209da917\"><strong>Tax base = 11/12 × 5000 </strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ece003e0-4123-4704-8c42-a0e8e7a35ec7\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"66a5396a-7258-43d4-92a7-f9c20f794950\"><strong>Total Fee</strong> and <strong>Total Fee VAT</strong> = <strong>5000 </strong>+ <strong>11/12 × 5000 × 12</strong>% = IDR 5,550</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"ma0wvpob-q56vry-036\">VAT Calculator</h2><p data-block-id=\"ma11v4po-jlvqz6-001\"><iframe src=\"https://xendit-vat-calculator.vercel.app\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"VAT Calculator\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;width:100%;height:800px;display:flex;margin:0 auto;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"801e855d-e7ae-4b59-86d0-606dab4f6fad\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ma0wves3-o0w6sf-035\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ma0w09ds-qtz2n7-026\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"fe521177-aabd-4e6c-9a5e-34166103baa1\"></h3><p data-block-id=\"058229be-230e-43e3-b268-591b8c8af002\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Value Added Tax (VAT)","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Pajak Pertambahan Nilai (PPN)","Slug":"value-added-tax-vat","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwl-yhtcso-454\">PPN (Pajak Pertambahan Nilai) adalah pajak konsumsi yang dikenakan atas barang dan jasa pada setiap tahap produksi atau distribusi. Tarif PPN bervariasi tergantung pada negara layanan, dan untuk layanan Xendit, biaya umumnya <strong>tidak termasuk PPN</strong>, yang berarti PPN akan ditambahkan ke biaya yang berlaku.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-5x82b9-455\">Penerapan PPN menurut negara</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-1u7v5o-456\">Xendit menerapkan PPN untuk semua layanan di negara-negara berikut:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-ecvqzp-457\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-izoy5o-458\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-9lk91p-459\"><strong>Indonesia</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-tku3wx-460\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-19y1vu-461\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-36dgjl-462\"><strong>Tarif PPN</strong>: 12% (Subtotal dikalikan dengan 11/12, sehingga tarif PPN efektif menjadi 11%)</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-m7t609-463\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-jxpr3y-464\"><strong>Malaysia</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-8okibs-465\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-z2d8p2-466\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-fa8gtq-467\"><strong>Setara PPN (SST)</strong>: 0%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-spivsv-468\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-k9cfqq-469\"><strong>Thailand</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-64ofgr-470\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-3m1a04-471\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-qm5xad-472\"><strong>Tarif PPN</strong>: 7%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-iqxsei-473\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-6fta9j-474\"><strong>Vietnam</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwm-wf61xz-475\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-ygfdm6-476\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-lwczvj-477\"><strong>Tarif PPN</strong>: 10%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-hclfel-478\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-voryi8-479\"><strong>Filipina</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-74w8fy-480\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-sb7pmv-481\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-q0vv4g-482\"><strong>Tarif PPN</strong>: 12%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-m34qg9-483\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-4lxzro-484\"><strong>Singapura</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-hix1kx-485\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-je9380-486\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-r11fk7-487\"><strong>Setara PPN (GST)</strong>: 0%</p></li></ul></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-93c431-488\">Perhitungan PPN</h3><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-7qjew4-489\">PPN dihitung atas <strong>biaya transaksi</strong> menggunakan tarif PPN yang berlaku untuk negara tempat layanan disediakan.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-ja3nsc-490\">Dalam hal <a href=\"/v1/docs/id/transaction-fees\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Direct Deduction</a>, jumlah ini akan langsung dipotong dari transaksi pada saat penyelesaian.</p><h4 data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-ptrra3-491\">Contoh perhitungan (Vietnam)</h4><ul data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-eqwq41-492\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwn-105k7t-493\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-n1ic6e-494\"><strong>Tarif Biaya</strong>: VND 2.500 per transaksi</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-22bvrn-495\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-3102oc-496\"><strong>PPN (10%)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-7xf88l-497\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-eo5597-498\"><strong>Total Biaya</strong> dan <strong>Total Biaya PPN</strong> = <strong>2500 </strong>+ <strong>2500 × 10</strong>% = VND 2.750</p></li></ul><h4 data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-rzlkcr-499\">Contoh perhitungan (Indonesia)</h4><ul data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-hjqylz-500\"><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-ogizib-501\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-o3d9jw-502\"><strong>Tarif Biaya</strong>: Rp 5.000 per transaksi</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-f6qmo4-503\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-7qqtfx-504\"><strong>PPN (12%)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-71nvvg-505\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-y6uzry-506\"><strong>Basis pajak = 11/12 × 5000 </strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-23glnz-507\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-bnjfzn-508\"><strong>Total Biaya</strong> dan <strong>Total Biaya PPN</strong> = <strong>5000 </strong>+ <strong>11/12 × 5000 × 12</strong>% = Rp 5.550</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-rioqn1-509\">Kalkulator PPN</h2><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwo-o1j6tj-510\"><iframe src=\"https://xendit-vat-calculator.vercel.app\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"VAT Calculator\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;width:100%;height:800px;display:flex;margin:0 auto;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwp-vncwc7-511\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwp-z0v6s8-512\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwp-47m00o-513\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwp-upqyjx-514\"></h3><p data-block-id=\"mcs4bzwp-e0tffm-515\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Pajak Pertambahan Nilai (PPN)","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ภาษีมูลค่าเพิ่ม (VAT)","Slug":"value-added-tax-vat","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"3de4393b-a5f0-4689-bb1b-786604688cfa\">VAT (Value-Added Tax) หรือภาษีมูลค่าเพิ่ม คือภาษีการบริโภคที่ใช้กับสินค้าและบริการในแต่ละขั้นตอนของการผลิตหรือการจัดจำหน่าย อัตรา VAT จะแตกต่างกันไปขึ้นอยู่กับประเทศที่ให้บริการ และสำหรับบริการของ Xendit โดยทั่วไปค่าธรรมเนียมจะ <strong>ไม่รวม VAT (VAT-exclusive)</strong> ซึ่งหมายความว่าจะมีการเพิ่ม VAT เข้าไปในค่าธรรมเนียมตามที่กำหนด</p><h2 data-block-id=\"96fc9bc1-351c-4379-8f42-f9f1869a8b1a\">การบังคับใช้ VAT ตามประเทศ</h2><p data-block-id=\"22aee218-4dc0-458d-afe4-29c287ba2a90\">Xendit ใช้ VAT กับบริการทั้งหมดในประเทศต่อไปนี้:</p><ol data-block-id=\"f704f5e7-0c9c-4289-8dde-b78227ffd86\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"712855e5-1fc9-41ec-8c88-5142860875b9\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"e71f381b-ea80-4a22-865b-8b5fd466f8f1\"><strong>อินโดนีเซีย (Indonesia)</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"cdaef5f6-b63e-40c5-b7c2-99ee4ec539b3\"><li data-block-id=\"a69d1814-f174-43cf-b5f2-94b1da3a5a04\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"485b40f7-9248-4632-98dc-a33d74e6c9f0\"><strong>อัตรา VAT (VAT Rate)</strong>: 12% (ยอดรวมย่อย (subtotal) จะถูกคูณด้วย 11/12 ทำให้มีอัตรา VAT ที่มีผลจริงเท่ากับ 11%)</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"3982e446-def7-4ebe-a059-620ac8464fc4\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"124bc150-d140-4c77-b3f5-0eaa689b7134\"><strong>มาเลเซีย (Malaysia)</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"02247e0f-ee75-4b5f-8464-df4dc0e90010\"><li data-block-id=\"921445d7-542e-4114-a05f-0eebde28b74f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"9f21b5b1-b049-4c27-9216-de16ffc0cbfa\"><strong>ภาษีที่เทียบเท่า VAT (VAT Equivalent (SST))</strong>: 0%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"00f4725d-b5a8-4a46-bbe6-553c67a4d0d1\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"a884c8a2-904d-45f2-a187-e6c329a3f481\"><strong>ไทย (Thailand)</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"40470f38-759d-4618-9213-1e691836906a\"><li data-block-id=\"43e47c6d-7d4e-436d-b5f9-400201c30fcb\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"bb866a6a-84e0-4966-94e5-8d552544dd26\"><strong>อัตรา VAT (VAT Rate)</strong>: 7%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"b8dfec48-e5b7-4439-977d-39387d8a49f3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"1a179519-ba60-42f2-9c95-d6c7eacd91f2\"><strong>เวียดนาม (Vietnam)</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"d6aea39f-9f54-4d51-8fbb-5b72f1127f20\"><li data-block-id=\"13c7ebfb-ec32-49f8-b58c-f9025dd1ca58\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"7bc138fa-801e-4c8c-acc8-997ebbbedf98\"><strong>อัตรา VAT (VAT Rate)</strong>: 10%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"82ac2318-c6af-49c8-ae2d-d4d86330fe10\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"bf6de06f-c1f8-4b5f-83c8-14aa24bfdb3e\"><strong>ฟิลิปปินส์ (Philippines)</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"36e0d766-97cd-4285-8b29-899702dd6fe0\"><li data-block-id=\"48dd45e0-02b7-4ce0-b2d1-2add4df55d71\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"c331eb3a-6b5d-4d23-a0de-7a2358dca1e5\"><strong>อัตรา VAT (VAT Rate)</strong>: 12%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"81b8c5d3-3b68-4bfb-a111-329a0d19426f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"35e1afa5-5160-41f4-86b9-af5435729de0\"><strong>สิงคโปร์ (Singapore)</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"e21b11b5-19ca-4c07-8682-ad197b40eda1\"><li data-block-id=\"b669980f-a1b8-4ee5-8a35-f03fd5740e2e\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"dd733af9-553f-4b0f-9aa0-21de7b72af5c\"><mark class=\"cd98f987-7aaf-4fee-b18e-9a991e91bd7d\" data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"cd98f987-7aaf-4fee-b18e-9a991e91bd7d\" data-resolved=\"true\"><strong>ภาษีที่เทียบเท่า VAT </strong></mark><strong>(GST)</strong>: 0%</p></li></ul></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"96a4fcd4-60dd-4689-8017-f937479be7d8\">การคำนวณ VAT</h3><p data-block-id=\"e7a7f1c9-f3fe-4275-83df-9fa59e5afd71\">VAT จะถูกคำนวณจาก <strong>ค่าธรรมเนียมการทำรายการ (transaction fee)</strong> โดยใช้อัตรา VAT ที่บังคับใช้สำหรับประเทศที่ให้บริการ</p><p data-block-id=\"e7a7f1c9-f3fe-4275-83df-9fa59e5afd71\">ในกรณีของ <a href=\"/v1/docs/transaction-fees\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Direct Deduction</a> จำนวนเงินนี้จะถูกหักโดยตรงจากการทำรายการเมื่อมีการชำระเงิน</p><h4 data-block-id=\"ma0wqppw-2evlwv-013\">ตัวอย่างการคำนวณ (เวียดนาม)</h4><ul data-block-id=\"ma0wqppw-0o5f3x-014\"><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-88j15p-017\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-kqpqkb-018\"><strong>อัตราค่าธรรมเนียม (Fee Rate)</strong>: VND 2,500 per transaction</p></li><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-ull3i9-019\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-9f737z-020\"><strong>VAT (10%)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-sl9cbv-023\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-9i5b5n-024\"><strong>ค่าธรรมเนียมรวม (Total Fee)</strong> และ <strong>VAT ค่าธรรมเนียมรวม (Total Fee VAT)</strong> = <strong>2500 </strong>+ <strong>2500 &#xd7; 10</strong>% = VND 2,750</p></li></ul><h4 data-block-id=\"6a7af58a-224b-463b-acc7-97041766f626\">ตัวอย่างการคำนวณ (อินโดนีเซีย)</h4><ul data-block-id=\"91499a2f-4421-4c55-8efa-4bf35c5139f7\"><li data-block-id=\"6f57ec42-3cbd-4363-8e7d-6812532c6037\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"4c2d5b3f-caf8-4c88-9130-1f39736b7e58\"><strong>อัตราค่าธรรมเนียม (Fee Rate)</strong>: IDR 5,000 per transaction</p></li><li data-block-id=\"636a3982-6a06-4ad9-bc07-bcf0988ecd4f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"b427231f-c9dd-4e89-baa2-29d9209da917\"><strong>VAT (12%)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"636a3982-6a06-4ad9-bc07-bcf0988ecd4f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"b427231f-c9dd-4e89-baa2-29d9209da917\"><strong>ฐานภาษี (Tax base) = 11/12 &#xd7; 5000 </strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ece003e0-4123-4704-8c42-a0e8e7a35ec7\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"66a5396a-7258-43d4-92a7-f9c20f794950\"><strong>ค่าธรรมเนียมรวม (Total Fee)</strong> และ <strong>VAT ค่าธรรมเนียมรวม (Total Fee VAT)</strong> = <strong>5000 </strong>+ <strong>11/12 &#xd7; 5000 &#xd7; 12</strong>% = IDR 5,550</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"ma0wvpob-q56vry-036\">เครื่องคำนวณ VAT</h2><p data-block-id=\"ma11v4po-jlvqz6-001\"><iframe src=\"https://xendit-vat-calculator.vercel.app\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"VAT Calculator\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;width:100%;height:800px;display:flex;margin:0 auto;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"801e855d-e7ae-4b59-86d0-606dab4f6fad\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ma0wves3-o0w6sf-035\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ma0w09ds-qtz2n7-026\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"fe521177-aabd-4e6c-9a5e-34166103baa1\"></h3><p data-block-id=\"058229be-230e-43e3-b268-591b8c8af002\"></p>","SeoTitle":"ภาษีมูลค่าเพิ่ม (VAT)","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Impuesto al Valor Agregado (IVA)","Slug":"value-added-tax-vat","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"3de4393b-a5f0-4689-bb1b-786604688cfa\">El IVA (Impuesto al Valor Agregado) es un impuesto al consumo aplicado a bienes y servicios en cada etapa de producción o distribución. La tasa de IVA varía según el país del servicio, y para los servicios de Xendit, las tarifas (fees) son generalmente **excluyentes de IVA** (VAT-exclusive), lo que significa que el IVA se agregará a las tarifas según corresponda.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"96fc9bc1-351c-4379-8f42-f9f1869a8b1a\">Aplicabilidad del IVA por país</h2><p data-block-id=\"22aee218-4dc0-458d-afe4-29c287ba2a90\">Xendit aplica el IVA a todos los servicios en los siguientes países:</p><ol data-block-id=\"f704f5e7-0c9c-4289-8dde-b782274ffd86\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"712855e5-1fc9-41ec-8c88-5142860875b9\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"e71f381b-ea80-4a22-865b-8b5fd466f8f1\"><strong>Indonesia</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"cdaef5f6-b63e-40c5-b7c2-99ee4ec539b3\"><li data-block-id=\"a69d1814-f174-43cf-b5f2-94b1da3a5a04\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"485b40f7-9248-4632-98dc-a33d74e6c9f0\"><strong>Tasa de IVA</strong>: 12% (El subtotal se multiplica por 11/12, lo que lleva la tasa de IVA efectiva al 11%)</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"3982e446-def7-4ebe-a059-620ac8464fc4\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"124bc150-d140-4c77-b3f5-0eaa689b7134\"><strong>Malaysia</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"02247e0f-ee75-4b5f-8464-df4dc0e90010\"><li data-block-id=\"921445d7-542e-4114-a05f-0eebde28b74f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"9f21b5b1-b049-4c27-9216-de16ffc0cbfa\"><strong>Equivalente de IVA (SST)</strong>: 0%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"00f4725d-b5a8-4a46-bbe6-553c67a4d0d1\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"a884c8a2-904d-45f2-a187-e6c329a3f481\"><strong>Thailand</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"40470f38-759d-4618-9213-1e691836906a\"><li data-block-id=\"43e47c6d-7d4e-436d-b5f9-400201c30fcb\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"bb866a6a-84e0-4966-94e5-8d552544dd26\"><strong>Tasa de IVA</strong>: 7%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"b8dfec48-e5b7-4439-977d-39387d8a49f3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"1a179519-ba60-42f2-9c95-d6c7eacd91f2\"><strong>Vietnam</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"d6aea39f-9f54-4d51-8fbb-5b72f1127f20\"><li data-block-id=\"13c7ebfb-ec32-49f8-b58c-f9025dd1ca58\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"7bc138fa-801e-4c8c-acc8-997ebbbedf98\"><strong>Tasa de IVA</strong>: 10%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"82ac2318-c6af-49c8-ae2d-d4d86330fe10\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"bf6de06f-c1f8-4b5f-83c8-14aa24bfdb3e\"><strong>Philippines</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"36e0d766-97cd-4285-8b29-899702dd6fe0\"><li data-block-id=\"48dd45e0-02b7-4ce0-b2d1-2add4df55d71\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"c331eb3a-6b5d-4d23-a0de-7a2358dca1e5\"><strong>Tasa de IVA</strong>: 12%</p></li></ul></li><li data-block-id=\"81b8c5d3-3b68-4bfb-a111-329a0d19426f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"35e1afa5-5160-41f4-86b9-af5435729de0\"><strong>Singapore</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"e21b11b5-19ca-4c07-8682-ad197b40eda1\"><li data-block-id=\"b669980f-a1b8-4ee5-8a35-f03fd5740e2e\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"dd733af9-553f-4b0f-9aa0-21de7b72af5c\"><mark class=\"cd98f987-7aaf-4fee-b18e-9a991e91bd7d\" data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"cd98f987-7aaf-4fee-b18e-9a991e91bd7d\" data-resolved=\"true\"><strong>Equivalente de IVA </strong></mark><strong>(GST)</strong>: 0%</p></li></ul></li></ol><h3 data-block-id=\"96a4fcd4-60dd-4689-8017-f937479be7d8\">Cálculo del IVA</h3><p data-block-id=\"e7a7f1c9-f3fe-4275-83df-9fa59e5afd71\">El IVA se calcula sobre la **tarifa de transacción** (transaction fee) utilizando la tasa de IVA aplicable para el país donde se proporciona el servicio.</p><p data-block-id=\"e7a7f1c9-f3fe-4275-83df-9fa59e5afd71\">En caso de <a href=\"/v1/docs/transaction-fees\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Deducción Directa</a> (Direct Deduction), este monto se deducirá directamente de la transacción en la liquidación (settlement).</p><h4 data-block-id=\"ma0wqppw-2evlwv-013\">Ejemplo de cálculo (Vietnam)</h4><ul data-block-id=\"ma0wqppw-0o5f3x-014\"><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-88j15p-017\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-kqpqkb-018\"><strong>Tasa de Tarifa</strong> (Fee Rate): VND 2,500 por transacción</p></li><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-ull3i9-019\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-9f737z-020\"><strong>IVA (10%)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-sl9cbv-023\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ma0wqppx-9i5b5n-024\"><strong>Tarifa Total</strong> (Total Fee) y <strong>IVA de Tarifa Total</strong> (Total Fee VAT) = <strong>2500 </strong>+ <strong>2500 &#xd7; 10</strong>% = VND 2,750</p></li></ul><h4 data-block-id=\"6a7af58a-224b-463b-acc7-97041766f626\">Ejemplo de cálculo (Indonesia)</h4><ul data-block-id=\"91499a2f-4421-4c55-8efa-4bf35c5139f7\"><li data-block-id=\"6f57ec42-3cbd-4363-8e7d-6812532c6037\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"4c2d5b3f-caf8-4c88-9130-1f39736b7e58\"><strong>Tasa de Tarifa</strong> (Fee Rate): IDR 5,000 por transacción</p></li><li data-block-id=\"636a3982-6a06-4ad9-bc07-bcf0988ecd4f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"b427231f-c9dd-4e89-baa2-29d9209da917\"><strong>IVA (12%)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"636a3982-6a06-4ad9-bc07-bcf0988ecd4f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"b427231f-c9dd-4e89-baa2-29d9209da917\"><strong>Base imponible = 11/12 &#xd7; 5000 </strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"ece003e0-4123-4704-8c42-a0e8e7a35ec7\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"66a5396a-7258-43d4-92a7-f9c20f794950\"><strong>Tarifa Total</strong> (Total Fee) y <strong>IVA de Tarifa Total</strong> (Total Fee VAT) = <strong>5000 </strong>+ <strong>11/12 &#xd7; 5000 &#xd7; 12</strong>% = IDR 5,550</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"ma0wvpob-q56vry-036\">Calculadora de IVA</h2><p data-block-id=\"ma11v4po-jlvqz6-001\"><iframe src=\"https://xendit-vat-calculator.vercel.app\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"VAT Calculator\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;width:100%;height:800px;display:flex;margin:0 auto;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p><p data-block-id=\"801e855d-e7ae-4b59-86d0-606dab4f6fad\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ma0wves3-o0w6sf-035\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ma0w09ds-qtz2n7-026\"></p><h3 data-block-id=\"fe521177-aabd-4e6c-9a5e-34166103baa1\"></h3><p data-block-id=\"058229be-230e-43e3-b268-591b8c8af002\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Impuesto al Valor Agregado (IVA)","Description":null}]